{"hash":"37089e2b0a44bdb463ce99748c6ea034eb28ebf2","data":{"tag":{"title":"cookie","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"기본적으로 사용하는 Cookie 옵션정리","path":"/7/","date":"2020. 09. 27","timeToRead":2,"description":"웹 개발시 기본이 되는 쿠키정보.","content":"<p>기본적인 로그인 기능이나 쇼핑몰에서 장바구니역할로 사용하는 Cookie는 <code>key=value</code> 값으로 구성되며, 세미콜론(;)으로 구분합니다.\n서버에서 <code>Set-Cookie</code> 헤더를 통해 생성할 수 있으며, 한글과 줄바꿈이 들어가게 될 경우 URLEncoding이 필요합니다.\n쿠키는 아래와 같은 옵션이 있으며, 브라우저에서의 개발툴에서도 확인가능합니다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>개발툴은 크롬, 파이어폭스등 잘 알려진 브라우저에서 F12를 기본 단축키로 쓰고 있습니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1248 1008' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-b8b676bdc5103efb1a27eb1bacd4b50f'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-b8b676bdc5103efb1a27eb1bacd4b50f)' width='1248' height='1008' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAA0CAYAAAA62j4JAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAJaklEQVRo3uVaSW8cxxXmTzBySyRyOPv0Mvu%2bcHbOPpzhKmqDHMkynKOihRRyCHIKkP8R2Npi5JCbrVycQBIpwIklRcrFyD%2bIBUSx1s/vvZ4eNYeUZNmEKY0a%2bFDLq%2bru99WrV/Wqe%2bJw6xwO1tZwuL6OQ/U1HGmdx%2brsGSyVTmG5/GvCIK2cwtHab3G2dwHn%2bhdwuvMxznQ/wek3EGcGOD1H6dwFrC1ckvrfHLiCc5Q/N39R8msLFzGxfHQBtWYL8/MLaHZaWDywhJlCFoFIEMFoiBCGPxxALBNDpdDF%2buIl/O7wX3C2cxlrvT8RrmzF3N7jbPcSzs7R%2b7Uu42z7As60P8ap5idY71/C%2bfYfsda9iPX5K1hfuIyJ3EwRqVRekC9UkcuVkM9XEY2mkEjmEIunkckUEI9nEItmkI/3kA11kQ2/DJ3niHSRizyvl3ykOyLriHy0XW5L35fJLf0J5dQiqukVFNrLaNZPYr5DVtz6AL3Gh0iv/B6V8nG08gdxuHEeE/VGB6n0DHIzJfT6S2h3%2buh05%2bEPhCHkZHKoVmvI5vKIRONQdBVTdhsmCWY6aSlPOaYFtgH22yaxb2q/yMwyY9ppp3RK8lw/OT2FX1A7Trm8b9DO6Dst/Tm/n%2bRGX0Nm3kvklOf%2bkXgUqqbD1vAhWKmivngSyyt9VLs9/PzkH6AX60inE5irnMDE51ev4tq16/jii7/hs88%2bx9Wrf8XGxibu3fs3bt26jdu371B6i1Ij/687d3H37r0tuEN1X3/9H3z66Z%2bJpIRYTTSaRCAYRak0i1K5hlgshXA4jkKRrawITQthJl8il